com.mci.model

Class TrainComponents

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.mci.model.TrainComponents
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    TrainInterface
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Locomotive, Wagon

    public abstract class TrainComponents
extends Object
implements TrainInterface
    Author:
    Negin Ashrafi Abstract base class representing a component of a train. This class implements the TrainInterface and provides methods to set and get information about the train component, such as its year, manufacturer, and serial number. It also defines pointers to the next and previous components in the train. Subclasses of this class can be used to represent different types of train components, such as locomotives, wagons, and cabooses.
